<a name="How to get numbered or not numbered headlines">

<H1>How to get numbered or not numbered headlines
</H1>


<P>
<B><U>Question:</U></B>
</P>


<P>
How can I get <A name="index_10_3"></A>numbered headlines and how can I suppress the numbering?
</P>


<P>
<B><U>Answer:</U></B>
</P>


<P>
This can be achieved by the <CODE>--num_headers</CODE> option and the <CODE>--nonum_headers</CODE> option respectively.
</P>


<P>
<B><U>Discussion:</U></B>
</P>


<P>
The <CODE>--nonum_headers</CODE> option may be used to overwrite the <CODE>--num_headers</CODE> option from a predefined style.
</P>


<P>

</P>
